    <title>Java 学习笔记：高效查找素数的埃氏筛法</title>
    <link href="/2026/04/16/Java%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0-%E7%B4%A0%E6%95%B0%E7%AD%9B/"/>
    <url>/2026/04/16/Java%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0-%E7%B4%A0%E6%95%B0%E7%AD%9B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在算法面试和日常编程中，查找一定范围内的所有素数是一个经典问题。相比于传统的逐个判断法，<strong>埃拉托斯特尼筛法（Sieve of Eratosthenes）</strong> 效率极高。本文将总结其核心思想并提供 Java 实现。</p><h2 id="1-核心思想"><a href="#1-核心思想" class="headerlink" title="1. 核心思想"></a>1. 核心思想</h2><p>埃氏筛的基本逻辑是：<strong>从最小的素数开始，将其所有的倍数（合数）标记出来并剔除。</strong></p><p>具体步骤如下：</p><ol><li>创建一个布尔数组，初始化 2 以上的所有数字为“待定素数”。</li><li>从最小的素数 <code>2</code> 开始，将其倍数（如 4, 6, 8, 10…）全部标记为“非素数”。</li><li>移动到下一个未被标记的数字（即 <code>3</code>），重复上述剔除过程。</li><li>优化：只需要筛选到 $\sqrt{n}$ 即可，因为更大的合数必然在之前已被较小的因数筛选过。</li></ol><h2 id="2-Java-代码实现"><a href="#2-Java-代码实现" class="headerlink" title="2. Java 代码实现"></a>2. Java 代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * 埃拉托斯特尼筛法实现</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * 功能：找出 2 到 max 之间的所有素数</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">PrimeSieve</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">max</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">120</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// isPrime[i] 代表数字 i 是否为素数</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">boolean</span>[] isPrime = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">boolean</span>[max + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>        <br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 1. 初始化：默认 2 及以上全部为素数</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; i &lt;= max; i++) &#123;<br>            isPrime[i] = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 2. 开始筛选</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 优化点：只需要遍历到 max 的平方根</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">p</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; p * p &lt;= max; p++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 如果当前数字没被剔除，说明它是素数</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (isPrime[p]) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-comment">// 将该素数的所有倍数标记为 false</span><br>                <span class="hljs-comment">// 从 p*p 开始剔除，因为之前的倍数（如 2p, 3p）已被更小的素数剔除过</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> p * p; i &lt;= max; i += p) &#123;<br>                    isPrime[i] = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 3. 结果输出</span><br>        System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;2 到 &quot;</span> + max + <span class="hljs-string">&quot; 之间的素数有：&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">count</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; i &lt;= max; i++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (isPrime[i]) &#123;<br>                System.out.print(i + <span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>);<br>                count++;<br>                <span class="hljs-comment">// 每 10 个换一行，保持排版美观</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (count % <span class="hljs-number">10</span> == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) System.out.println();<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-复杂度分析"><a href="#3-复杂度分析" class="headerlink" title="3. 复杂度分析"></a>3. 复杂度分析</h2><ul><li><strong>时间复杂度</strong>：$O(n \log \log n)$。这接近于线性时间，比逐个判断的 $O(n\sqrt{n})$ 要快得多。</li><li><strong>空间复杂度</strong>：$O(n)$。需要一个长度为 $n+1$ 的布尔数组来存储标记状态。</li></ul><h2 id="4-总结与反思"><a href="#4-总结与反思" class="headerlink" title="4. 总结与反思"></a>4. 总结与反思</h2><p>埃氏筛是“空间换时间”思想的典型应用。通过一次性标记，避免了对每个数字进行大量的除法运算。在处理百万级别范围内的素数查找时，这种算法的优势会非常明显。</p><pre><code class="hljs">### 操作小贴士：* **文件名建议**：你可以直接保存为 `source/_posts/Java学习笔记-素数筛.md`。* **部署发布**：执行 `hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d` 即可完成更新。</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
